      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything just feels so pointless lately. i was looking at the stars tonight and it just hit me that in a few billion years the sun is gonna die and everything we've ever done or felt or been will literally just be nothing. like, why even bother trying to build a life or struggle through anything when the end result is just total emptiness? it feels like we're just playing a game that's rigged to end in zero.",
